         <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">WORLD CUP 2018 - V\u00d2NG B\u1ea2NG</span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"border:1px solid #dddddd;\">\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center;\">18/06 19:00</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n - H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">18/06 22:00</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">B\u1ec9 - Panama</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"border:1px solid #dddddd;\">\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center;\">19/06 01:00</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">Anh - Tunisia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"295","checkdouble":"188783"},{"date":"07:29 18/06","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: S\u1ef1 th\u1eadt n\u00e0o sau t\u1ea5m m\u00e0n nhung?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/du-am-sai-gon-52-ha-noi-su-that-nao-sau-tam-man-nhung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong c\u01a1n m\u01b0a n\u1eb7ng h\u1ea1t t\u1ea1i Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t chi\u1ec1u qua, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u00fac th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang x\u1ebfp \u00e1p ch\u00f3t tr\u00ean BXH l\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 n\u1ebfu x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c hai \u0111\u1ed9i?</h2><br>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: M\u1ed9t tr\u1eddi m\u1ed9t v\u1ef1c<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018-372-188725.html\" target=\"_blank\">S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i </span>t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111ang n\u1eafm gi\u1eef k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 13 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau 11 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a t\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. N\u1ebfu t\u00ednh th\u00eam c\u1ea3 V-League 2017 v\u00e0 m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn c\u00fap QG 2018 th\u00ec m\u1ea1ch tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00e9o d\u00e0i n\u00ean con s\u1ed1 20.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 36 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 7 b\u00e0n sau 13 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng m\u1ea1nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i V-League, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng, Thanh H\u00f3a hay HAGL. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t d\u00e0n n\u1ed9i binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, tr\u1ebb kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 khao kh\u00e1t nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t Moses gi\u00e0u c\u01a1 b\u1eafp khu trung tuy\u1ebfn v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Oseni \u0111ang l\u00e0 hung th\u1ea7n v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 V-League.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i S\u1ef1 th\u1eadt n\u00e0o sau t\u1ea5m m\u00e0n nhung h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i S\u1ef1 th\u1eadt n\u00e0o sau t\u1ea5m m\u00e0n nhung h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Sau-vong-14-V-League-2018-Ha-Noi,-HAGL-dong-loat-nga-ngua-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Quang H\u1ea3i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh nh\u1eadp t\u1ecbch Ho\u00e0ng V\u0169 Samson \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ghi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 4-1 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 13. V\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f9ng h\u1eadu nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u00edt ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd r\u1eb1ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u1ea1i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng V-League tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC c\u1ee7a Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi 7 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, trong \u0111\u00f3 bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp su\u1ea5t xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng l\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh FC \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 13.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ecd ghi 15 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 23 b\u00e0n. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n thua nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec gi\u1ea3i, ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean con s\u1ed1 24 b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 l\u1ea1i theo m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eadm v\u00e0 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1eady m\u00e0 trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng ai \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec. Trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c di\u1ec7n thanh l\u00fd v\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m l\u00e0 Da Sylva l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u00e3 &lsquo;v\u01b0\u01a1n vai&rsquo; \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u00f4ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ea1y cho H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC h\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf V-League 2018, m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i m\u00e0 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay 12 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i v\u1eabn \u0111ang m\u01a1 nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u00f3 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ea1ch?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi xa l\u1ea1 vi\u1ec7c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n hay SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 &lsquo;anh em m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0&rsquo; d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ed7 Quang Hi\u1ec3n. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed S\u00e0i G\u00f2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u1eddi \u0111\u00f4 v\u00e0o Nam c\u0169ng t\u1eebng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby v\u00e0 t\u1eebng n\u1eb1m d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Nguy\u1ec5n Giang \u0110\u00f4ng, c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi l\u00e0 b\u1ed1 v\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ee3i d\u00e2y r\u00e0ng bu\u1ed9c t\u1ea1i V-League. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 &lsquo;ru\u1ed9t th\u1ecbt&rsquo; nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e9p d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn 100% tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u trung th\u1ef1c, cao th\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ha Noi thua dam Sai Gon o vong 14 V-League 2018.\" title=\"H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/hlv-chu-dinh-nghiem-phu-nhan-viec-ha-noi-thua-dam-vi-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ea1ch \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng, Bongda24h xin kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 n\u00eau ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c quan t\u00e2m sau v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra chuy\u1ec7n cho \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i V-League. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f3m l\u1ea1i, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-2 c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c m\u1edbi hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sau-vong-14-vleague-2018-ha-noi-hagl-dong-loat-nga-ngua-168-188775.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/sau-vong-14-vleague-2018-ha-noi-hagl-dong-loat-nga-ngua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sau-vong-14-vleague-2018-ha-noi-hagl-dong-loat-nga-ngua-168-188775.html\">Sau v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018: H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HAGL \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a</span><br>\r\nV\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u1ed1c khi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ch\u1ecbu thua \u0111\u1ed9i \u00e1p ch\u00f3t tr\u00ean BXH l\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC c\u00f2n HAGL ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a tr\u00ean s\u00e2n SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. N\u00f3...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-chu-dinh-nghiem-phu-nhan-viec-ha-noi-thua-dam-vi-world-cup-2018-291-188754.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-chu-dinh-nghiem-phu-nhan-viec-ha-noi-thua-dam-vi-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-chu-dinh-nghiem-phu-nhan-viec-ha-noi-thua-dam-vi-world-cup-2018-291-188754.html\">HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm v\u00ec World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nHLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm c\u00f3 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb World Cup 2018, \u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng ch\u00ednh kh\u00e1t khao c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018-372-188725.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018-372-188725.html\">S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i (KT): Da Sylva l\u1eadp poker, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0110\u00f4 thua tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i V-League 2018</span><br>\r\nB\u1ed1n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Da Sylva \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap cho S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC gi\u00e0nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng 5-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. Thua tr\u1eadn, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t m\u1ea1ch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf con s\u1ed1 13.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"294","checkdouble":"188784"},{"date":"07:30 18/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (19h00 ng\u00e0y 18/6): X\u1ee9 kim chi kh\u00f3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/nhan-dinh-thuy-dien-vs-han-quoc-19h00-ngay-186-xu-kim-chi-kho-gay-bat-ngo.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng F, b\u1edfi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 Mexico \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110KV\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0. Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A, sau Ph\u00e1p. D\u00f9 c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 v\u1edbi H\u00e0 Lan (19) nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean v\u00ec h\u01a1n ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5. V\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Janne Andersson gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 v\u00f2ng play-off v\u1edbi Italia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (19h00 ng\u00e0y 186) - B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (19h00 ng\u00e0y 186) - B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/Thuy-Dien-vs-Han-Quoc-(19h00-ngay-186)---Bang-F-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Italia \u1edf v\u00f2ng play-off</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n khi lo\u1ea1i Italia \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. N\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng F v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c, Mexcico v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Andersson l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf b\u1ea3ng F. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/duc-vs-mexico-bang-f-463-188732.html\" target=\"_blank\">Mexico \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110KV\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c</span> v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0. V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ho\u1eb7c H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSo v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Zlatan Ibrahimovic, song l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Andersson d\u1eabn d\u1eaft l\u00fac n\u00e0y t\u1ecf ra g\u1eafn k\u1ebft, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt \u0111ang l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 then ch\u1ed1t \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Marcus Berg l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc \u00c2u. \u1ede v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ghi t\u1edbi 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Thuy Dien vs Han Quoc\" title=\"Preview Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Thuy-Dien-vs-Han-Quoc.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc \u00c2u bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tay HLV Janne Andersson \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xen k\u1ebd gi\u1eefa s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m. H\u1ecd s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Victor Lindelof, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Martin Olsson, Sebastian Larsson hay Mikael Lustig c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc \u00c2u.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t cho World Cup 2018, 2 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a 0-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Peru.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 HLV Andersson kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n nh\u1eefng mi\u1ebfng \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ph\u00e1t huy nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n cho nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf VCK World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n lu\u00f4n ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. Trong 4 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc \u00c2u b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMexico \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c, b\u1edfi v\u1eady Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t \u1edf b\u1ea3ng F.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00f3, g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn HLV Janne Andersson s\u1ebd l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eafp s\u00e1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Son Heung-min, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Tottenham.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Han Quoc 1-3 Bosnia\" title=\"H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 1-3 Bosnia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/1/han-quoc-13-bosnia-nhung-chien-binh-taeguk-chet-ngay-tren-san-nha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Spurs, song m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh anh r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n \u1edf b\u1ea3ng F.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, b\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1 trong 6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Shin Tae-yong, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u01a1i thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. \u1ede b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c, Mexico v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn x\u1ee9 kim chi s\u1ebd \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng \u1edf t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi duy nh\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i sao Son Heung-min tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<div><strong>Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n (4-4-2):</strong> 1.Olsen; 2.Lustig, 3.Lindelof, 4.Granqvist, 6.Augustinsson; 17.Claesson, 7.Larsson, 8.Ekdal, 10.Forsberg; 20.Toivonen, 9.Berg</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n<strong>H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (4-2-3-1):</strong> 1.Seung-gyu; 2.Lee Yong, 20.Hyun-soo, 3.Seung-hyun; 14.Hong Chul; 15.Woo-young, 16.Sung-yueng; 17.Jae-sung, 7.Son, 11.Hee-chan; 9.Shin-wook</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: 2-0</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Thuy Dien vs Han Quoc\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Thuy-Dien-vs-Han-Quoc-(4-4-2-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"293","checkdouble":"188785"},{"date":"08:29 18/06","title":"Chicharito v\u1eeba kh\u00f3c v\u1eeba m\u1ebfu m\u00e1o: \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/chicharito-chien-thang-truoc-duc-khong-chi-mang-tinh-lich-su.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chicharito ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico, c\u1ef1u sao MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap Mexico thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed m\u00e0 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y th\u1eafp s\u00e1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mexico xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c 1-0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nT\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018, Mexico c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi \u0110KV\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n, song \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u M\u1ef9 l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chicharito ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chicharito ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Chicharito-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Duc-vs-Mexico-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T Mexico \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c 1-0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nMexico duy tr\u00ec m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, h\u1ecd h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u1ed1i \u0111a s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f2n t\u1ecf ra hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nT\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh Hirving Lozano \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Mexico \u1edf ph\u00fat 35. Th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i, \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-duc-vs-mexico-bang-f-421-188747.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico</span> gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u M\u1ef9 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf b\u1ea3ng F, b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 H\u00e0 Qu\u1ed1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chicharito x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chicharito ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico, c\u1ef1u sao MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap Mexico thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed m\u00e0 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y th\u1eafp s\u00e1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chicharito v\u1eeba kh\u00f3c v\u1eeba m\u1ebfu m\u00e1o Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Chicharito v\u1eeba kh\u00f3c v\u1eeba m\u1ebfu m\u00e1o Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/chicharito-chien-thang-truoc-duc-khong-chi-mang-tinh-lich-su.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chicharito x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vui m\u1eebng sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u NHM kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi, l\u00fac n\u00e0y t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n&ldquo;Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c mang t\u00ednh l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, n\u00f3 gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c gi\u00fap Mexico m\u1edf toang c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp trung tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2, Mexico s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng F. N\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, h\u1ecd g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm ch\u1eafc t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span><br />\r\n</strong><br />\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/17/Duc-0-1-Mexico.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"292","checkdouble":"188786"},{"date":"08:59 18/06","title":"\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/doi-truong-thuy-sy-danh-gia-cao-1-diem-co-duoc-truoc-brazil.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Stephan Lichtsteiner ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9, ng\u00f4i sao v\u1eeba c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lichtsteiner \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y s\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 b\u1ecb Brazil \u00e9p s\u00e2n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 1-1. V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Stephan Lichtsteiner ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Stephan Lichtsteiner ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/doi-truong-thuy-sy-danh-gia-cao-1-diem-co-duoc-truoc-brazil.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lichtsteiner n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2, Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Serbia, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Costa Rica 1-0 trong tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng F. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia, c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nStephan Lichtsteiner ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9, ng\u00f4i sao v\u1eeba c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c1 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i. Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00e1t huy \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u00fac m\u1eebng c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00ec m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 \u0103n m\u1eebng v\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lichtsteiner tin Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9, Lichtsteiner c\u0169ng t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Brazil vs Thuy Sy\" title=\"Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/tong-hop-brazil-11-thuy-sy-bang-e-world-cup-2018.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lichtsteiner tin</span>\u00a0Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y s\u1ef9. 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil\u00a0gi\u00fap Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 th\u1eafng s\u00e1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Serbia \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 chi\u1ebfm t\u1edbi 80% c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Serbia r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, b\u1edfi v\u1eady ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/hlv-thuy-sy-noi-gi-sau-chien-tich-cam-hoa-brazil-421-188781.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Vladimir Petkovic c\u0169ng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Brazil</span>, \u00f4ng tin r\u1eb1ng 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Selecao s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 th\u1eafp s\u00e1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 (B\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018)<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span><br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/18/Brazil-1-1-Thuy-Sy.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"291","checkdouble":"188787"},{"date":"08:43 18/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Panama (22h00 ng\u00e0y 18/6): Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ra oai","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/18/bi-vs-panama-22h00-ngay-186-quy-do-ra-oai.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng G, nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u tham d\u1ef1 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Panama t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nB\u1ec9 tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u201cb\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea1o\u201d c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh h\u1ecd v\u1edbi PSG trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ea7y r\u1eaby si\u00eau sao v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf gi\u1edd \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ee9ng ngang h\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i gia c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111e d\u1ecda b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai. H\u1ecd xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. H\u1ecd ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t (c\u00f9ng 43 b\u00e0n nh\u01b0 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c), \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi l\u00e0 1 trong 4 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i (c\u00f9ng Anh, \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0110T B\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t \u00f4ng l\u1edbn th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh theo n\u0103m th\u00e1ng. L\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u201cth\u1eeba m\u1ee9a\u201d v\u00e0 d\u1ea1n d\u00e0y kinh nghi\u1ec7m chinh chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec9nh cao t\u1eeb Anh sang \u00dd, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u mong ch\u1edd Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd b\u00f9ng ch\u00e1y t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, sau 2 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Panama b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Panama b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/Nhan-dinh-Bi-vs-Panama-bang-G-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T B\u1ec9 s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh t\u00e0i k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1eb3ng th\u1ebf m\u00e0, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Eden Hazard li\u00ean t\u1ee5c l\u00ean b\u00e1o n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u2013 cho kh\u1ecfi b\u00f5\u2026 th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng. Ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ebf m\u00e0, Kevin De Bruyne trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, \u0111\u1ea7y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c ch\u00fat n\u1eefa cho \u0111\u00e0n em Januzaj v\u00e0o b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Roberto Martinez th\u00ec ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ec1 b\u1eadn t\u00e2m, tr\u00e1i l\u1ea1i \u00f4ng c\u00f2n\u2026 m\u1eebng r\u1ee1 v\u00ec c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tinh th\u1ea7n m\u00e1u l\u1eeda, d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eb7t tham v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn \u2013 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c\u2026 \u0110T Anh. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eady, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ea7m trong b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 th\u1edf v\u1edbi duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 Tam S\u01b0, th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t \u0110T B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0110T Anh \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Khi \u0111\u00f3, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thu th\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama v\u00e0 Tunisia. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, nh\u01b0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m tay th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Martinez.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Panama (22h00 ng\u00e0y 186) Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ra oai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Panama (22h00 ng\u00e0y 186) Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ra oai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/Nhan-dinh-Bi-vs-Panama-(22h00-ngay-186)-Quy-do-ra-oai-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Panama kh\u00f3 tho\u00e1t ph\u1eadn l\u00f3t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u1edbi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tham d\u1ef1 VCK World Cup, Panama \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1ea3 \u0110T M\u1ef9 tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u201cTh\u1ee7y tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ecf\u201d \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc gi\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 trong 3 t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 c\u1ee7a khu v\u1ef1c CONCACAF, qua \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh, c\u00f9ng \u201cng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n\u201d Iceland.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, 4 tri\u1ec7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Trung M\u1ef9 c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o, d\u00f9 v\u1eady tham d\u1ef1 World Cup v\u1edbi Panama v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i du l\u1ecbch \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a. Gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 t\u1edbi Nga \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n Hernan Dario Gomez, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau xa h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Panama b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Roman Torres c\u1ee7a Panama n\u1eb7ng 99kg\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/Nhung-thong-tin,-thong-ke-thu-vi-ve-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Panama \u0103n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m, hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u2013 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00edch \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eeba t\u1ea7m v\u1edbi n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, khi h\u1ecd n\u1eb1m trong b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Ngo\u00e0i \u0110T B\u1ec9 nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i \u1edf tr\u00ean, c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 \u0110T Anh \u2013 \u00f4ng l\u1edbn ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 Tunisia \u2013 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u Phi x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng cao nh\u1ea5t FIFA.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ec5 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Panama kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd trong gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 khung th\u00e0nh c\u00e0ng l\u00e2u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n nh\u1edb trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup khu v\u1ef1c CONCACAF, \u0110T Panama \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e1ch qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p, l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u201cb\u00e0n th\u1eafng ma\u201d c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gabriel Torres. Nh\u01b0ng v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p qu\u1ef7 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Panama b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Preview B\u1ec9 vs Panama\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Bi-vs-Panama.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Panama b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng tin b\u00ean l\u1ec1<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean B\u1ec9 vs Panama ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi nhau.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- B\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 9/10 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup, ghi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 b\u00e0n m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 thua 1 trong 9 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1986.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- B\u1ec9 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn. 8 b\u00e0n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1ea1i World Cup \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb sau ph\u00fat 70.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- B\u1ec9 b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup khu v\u1ef1c ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Lukaku ghi 11 b\u00e0n trong 8 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup (khu v\u1ef1c ch\u00e2u \u00c2u), ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m m\u1ed7i Lewandowski v\u00e0 Cris Ronaldo, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Panama (9 b\u00e0n).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Gabriel Torres v\u00e0 Roman Torres l\u00e0 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n nh\u1ea5t cho Panama \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i (2 b\u00e0n).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Panama l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Panama gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 World Cup v\u1edbi hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 -1, ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 3/10 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- HLV Hernan Dario Gomez c\u1ee7a Panama \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft 3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n tham d\u1ef1 World Cup (2 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Colombia v\u00e0 Ecuador).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 Kompany l\u1eabn Vermarlen ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3 trung v\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Boyata, Alderweireld v\u00e0 Vertonghen. Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Panama c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ec9 (3-4-3)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1.Courtois</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2.Alderweireld \u2013 20.Boyata \u2013 3.Vertonghen</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">15.Meunier \u2013 7.Bruyne \u2013 6.Witsel \u2013 11.Carrasco</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">14.Mertens \u2013 9.Lukaku \u2013 10.Hazard</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Panama (5-4-1)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1.Penedo</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2.Murillo \u2013 13.Machado \u2013 5.Torres \u2013 4.Escobar \u2013 17.Ovalle</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">19.Avila \u2013 20.Godoy \u2013 6.Gomez \u2013 8.Barcenas</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">9.Torres</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h2>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 B\u1ec9 vs Panama: 4-0</h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-10-nhan-dinh-bang-g-421-188564.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-10-nhan-dinh-bang-g.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-10-nhan-dinh-bang-g-421-188564.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 10: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea3ng G</span><br>\r\nS\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 10 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 Bongda24h.vn t\u1edbi v\u1edbi c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn t\u1ed5ng quan v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3ng G c\u1ee7a hai \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch l\u00e0 Anh v\u00e0 B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/doi-tuyen-bi-tham-du-world-cup-2018-the-he-vang-da-du-cho-cup-vang-421-188246.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/11/doi-tuyen-bi-tham-du-world-cup-2018-the-he-vang-da-du-cho-cup-vang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/doi-tuyen-bi-tham-du-world-cup-2018-the-he-vang-da-du-cho-cup-vang-421-188246.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018: Th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 cho c\u00fap v\u00e0ng?</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eddi s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, B\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng ti\u1ebfn xa \u1edf World Cup 2018, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 \u0111\u0103ng quang...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"290","checkdouble":"188789"},{"date":"02:11 18/06","title":"HLV Joachim Low: \"\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/hlv-joachim-low-dt-duc-se-khong-thay-doi-loi-choi.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Joachim Low kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ec3 thua Mexico trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/17/Duc-0-1-Mexico.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nB\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Mexico. Hirving Lozano ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Mannschaft. \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c sau \u0111\u00f3 d\u00f9 d\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u00ean cao nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n khi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Mexico rung l\u00ean.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Joachim Low khang dinh DT Duc se khong thay doi loi choi du de thua Mexico.\" title=\"HLV Joachim Low kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Mexico.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/hlv-joachim-low-dt-duc-se-khong-thay-doi-loi-choi.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Joachim Low kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Mexico.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nL\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed7i lo khi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng trong vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. Ngo\u00e0i ra, h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed1i lo c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c khi ch\u01a1i b\u1ebf t\u1eafc, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c trong nh\u1eefng pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c thua trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau tr\u1eadn thua Algeria v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1982.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, HLV Joachim Low kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i: &quot;Trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi khi. \u0110\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7p hai, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh&quot;.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;\u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1eb3n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, \u00fd t\u00f4i l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng b\u1eaft nh\u1ecbp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p l\u1ef1c. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i. \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn c\u00f2n hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n (1h00 ng\u00e0y 24/6) v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (21h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6).<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/duc-vs-mexico-bang-f-463-188732.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/ket-qua-duc-vs-mexico-bang-f.png\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/duc-vs-mexico-bang-f-463-188732.html\">\u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico (KT): Nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i to\u00e0n t\u1eadp ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span><br />\r\nNh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 trong h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 cup v\u00e0ng khi ph\u01a1i \u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico, \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t xu\u1ed1ng phong \u0111\u1ed9.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"289","checkdouble":"188760"},{"date":"03:09 18/06","title":"S\u00e1t th\u1ee7 Lozano n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/sat-thu-lozano-noi-gi-sau-khi-choc-thung-luoi-dt-duc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Hirving Lozano \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c.</h2><h2>Hirving Lozano ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ngay \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup 2018, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a Mexico mong mu\u1ed1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f2n h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Trung M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf \u1edf b\u1ea3ng F.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lozano DT Mexico\" title=\"Lozano \u0110T Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/sat-thu-lozano-noi-gi-sau-khi-choc-thung-luoi-dt-duc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Hirving Lozano ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap \u0110T Mexico \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Hirving Lozano h\u1ed3 h\u1edfi cho hay: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Mexico hay kh\u00f4ng. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Mexico s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 t\u00f4i t\u1eebng ghi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 bao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1u m\u01a1 \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup. Vi\u1ec7c ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u00f3 th\u1eadt c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 22, Lozano \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Mexico. &lsquo;C\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c&rdquo; \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 29 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o &ldquo;El Tri&rdquo; v\u00e0 ghi 8 b\u00e0n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9, Lozano ra s\u00e2n g\u1ea7n 150 tr\u1eadn cho Pachuca v\u00e0 PSV, ghi 48 b\u00e0n. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 3 n\u0103m, ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y c\u0169ng t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man United theo \u0111u\u1ed5i, tuy nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 v\u00ec sao cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb b\u1ecf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Hirving Lozano.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Highlight: \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/17/Duc-0-1-Mexico.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#222222;mso-fareast-language:KO\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"288","checkdouble":"188761"},{"date":"02:30 18/06","title":"Ivanovic ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c trong ng\u00e0y Serbia gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/ivanovic-pha-ky-luc-trong-ngay-serbia-gianh-chien-thang-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico, HLV Juan Carlos Osorio th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed k\u00edp gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ed1i 17/6.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Juan Carlos Osorio b\u1eadt m\u00ed chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Mexico tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f9ng h\u1eadu c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Mexico v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-1 t\u1ea1i Confed Cup 2017 tuy nhi\u00ean \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u chung cu\u1ed9c.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Juan Carlos Osorio DT Mexico\" title=\"HLV Juan Carlos Osorio \u0110T Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/hlv-mexico-bat-mi-yeu-to-giup-mexico-danh-bai-dt-duc.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Juan Carlos Osorio \u0103n m\u1eebng c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 sau tr\u1eadn&nbsp;\u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u1ebb Hirving Lozano, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Mexico \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup 2018, khi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n l\u00e0 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u00f9ng h\u1eadu. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, HLV Juan Carlos Osorio c\u1ee7a Mexico t\u00e2m s\u1ef1: &ldquo;Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00ec \u0110T Mexico \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n trong hi\u1ec7p 1. Sang t\u1edbi hi\u1ec7p 2, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi s\u1ebd d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mexico c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh t\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Mario Gomez \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. H\u00f4m qua ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 4 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ph\u00eda tr\u00ean. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch gi\u00fap Mexico su\u00fdt c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay&rdquo;. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Mexico thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 57 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia n\u00f3i th\u00eam: &ldquo;T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd ra s\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng b\u1ea3o h\u1ecd r\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ecbu m\u1ecdi s\u1ee9c \u00e9p ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 t\u00f4i, c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. N\u1ebfu th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00f2n thua th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u00f4m nay h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c, Mexico \u0111ang tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. H\u1ecd th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u01afCV n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd nh\u1ea5t cho ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch l\u00e0 Brazil.<br />\r\n<strong>Video: \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</strong><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span><br />\r\n<img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height: 220px;\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sat-thu-lozano-noi-gi-sau-khi-choc-thung-luoi-dt-duc-421-188761.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/sat-thu-lozano-noi-gi-sau-khi-choc-thung-luoi-dt-duc.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sat-thu-lozano-noi-gi-sau-khi-choc-thung-luoi-dt-duc-421-188761.html\">S\u00e1t th\u1ee7 Lozano n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c?</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Hirving Lozano \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thua-mexico-mats-hummels-ly-giai-viec-hang-thu-dt-duc-choi-te-465-188763.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/thua-mexico-mats-hummels-ly-giai-viec-hang-thu-dt-duc-choi-te.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thua-mexico-mats-hummels-ly-giai-viec-hang-thu-dt-duc-choi-te-465-188763.html\">Thua Mexico, Mats Hummels l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7</span><br />\r\nMats Hummels \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn thua Mexico.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thua-mexico-dt-duc-vuong-loi-nguyen-nha-vo-dich-tai-world-cup-465-188759.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/thua-mexico-dt-duc-vuong-loi-nguyen-nha-vo-dich-tai-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thua-mexico-dt-duc-vuong-loi-nguyen-nha-vo-dich-tai-world-cup-465-188759.html\">Thua Mexico, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u01b0\u1edbng l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i World Cup</span><br />\r\n\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ee9 ba li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp sau khi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 thua Mexico.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-duc-vs-mexico-vinh-danh-nhung-nguoi-dan-ong-dung-cam-421-188758.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/du-am-duc-vs-mexico-vinh-danh-nhung-nguoi-dan-ong-dung-cam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-duc-vs-mexico-vinh-danh-nhung-nguoi-dan-ong-dung-cam-421-188758.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico: Vinh danh nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m</span><br />\r\nD\u01b0 \u00e2m \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a khu v\u1ef1c CONCACAF. C\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Mexico \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eddi v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng noi g\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-duc-01-mexico-421-188757.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-duc-01-mexico.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-duc-01-mexico-421-188757.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico</span><br />\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng F VCK World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"287","checkdouble":"188762"},{"date":"02:51 18/06","title":"Thua Mexico, Mats Hummels l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/thua-mexico-mats-hummels-ly-giai-viec-hang-thu-dt-duc-choi-te.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mats Hummels \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn thua Mexico.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/17/Duc-0-1-Mexico.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<br />\r\nH\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c bi\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico. Trong khi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ebf t\u1eafc, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c th\u00ec h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y bu\u1ed3n khi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 Mexico khu\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ea3o.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thua Mexico, Mats Hummels l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thua Mexico, Mats Hummels l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/thua-mexico-mats-hummels-ly-giai-viec-hang-thu-dt-duc-choi-te.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Mats Hummels l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 trong tr\u1eadn thua Mexico.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nSau khi nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, Mats Hummels l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico: &quot;Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecdc l\u00f3t c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n t\u00f4i v\u1edbi Jerome Boateng \u1edf ph\u00eda sau. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1eeb v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u y nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Saudi Arabia, ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch cho nh\u1eefng g\u00ec di\u1ec5n ra trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t, Mexico hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;V\u1edbi b\u1ea3y \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00e1m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n&quot; - Hummels nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: &quot;Nh\u01b0ng nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i v\u1eabn hay n\u00f3i, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 qu\u1ea3 ng\u1ecdt. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ee9c t\u1ec9nh qu\u00e1 mu\u1ed9n. \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng hai tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i&quot;.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y tung ra \u0111\u1ebfn 25 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong ba \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Argentina (27, 1-1 vs Iceland) v\u00e0 Peru (17, 0-1 vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch).<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn c\u00f2n hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n (1h00 ng\u00e0y 24/6) v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (21h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6).<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/duc-vs-mexico-bang-f-463-188732.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/ket-qua-duc-vs-mexico-bang-f.png\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/duc-vs-mexico-bang-f-463-188732.html\">\u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico (KT): Nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i to\u00e0n t\u1eadp ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span><br />\r\nNh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 trong h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 cup v\u00e0ng khi ph\u01a1i \u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico, \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t xu\u1ed1ng phong \u0111\u1ed9.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"286","checkdouble":"188763"},{"date":"03:00 18/06","title":"T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 (B\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/tong-hop-brazil-11-thuy-sy-bang-e-world-cup-2018.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft bao nhi\u00eau c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n song r\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c c\u00e1c v\u0169 c\u00f4ng Samba ch\u1ec9 thu v\u1ec1 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</h2><strong>B\u1ea2N QUY\u1ec0N VTV</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nBrazil: </strong>Alisson, Danilo, Thiago Silva, Miranda, Marcelo (c), Paulinho, Casemiro, Coutinho, Willian, Gabriel Jesus, Neymar.<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9: </strong>Yann Sommer, Stephan Lichtsteiner (c), Fabian  Schar, Manuel Akanji, Ricardo Rodriguez, Valon Behrami, Granit Xhaka,  Xherdan Shaqiri, Blerim Dzemaili, Steven Zuber, Haris Seferovic.<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"285","checkdouble":"188764"},{"date":"03:32 18/06","title":"HLV Carlos Osorio b\u1eadt m\u00ed y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 gi\u00fap Mexico \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/hlv-mexico-bat-mi-yeu-to-giup-mexico-danh-bai-dt-duc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico, HLV Juan Carlos Osorio th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed k\u00edp gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ed1i 17/6.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Juan Carlos Osorio b\u1eadt m\u00ed chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Mexico tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f9ng h\u1eadu c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Mexico v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-1 t\u1ea1i Confed Cup 2017 tuy nhi\u00ean \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u chung cu\u1ed9c.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Juan Carlos Osorio DT Mexico\" title=\"HLV Juan Carlos Osorio \u0110T Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/hlv-mexico-bat-mi-yeu-to-giup-mexico-danh-bai-dt-duc.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Juan Carlos Osorio \u0103n m\u1eebng c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 sau tr\u1eadn&nbsp;\u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u1ebb Hirving Lozano, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Mexico \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup 2018, khi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n l\u00e0 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u00f9ng h\u1eadu. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, HLV Juan Carlos Osorio c\u1ee7a Mexico t\u00e2m s\u1ef1: &ldquo;Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00ec \u0110T Mexico \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n trong hi\u1ec7p 1. Sang t\u1edbi hi\u1ec7p 2, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi s\u1ebd d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mexico c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh t\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Mario Gomez \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. H\u00f4m qua ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 4 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ph\u00eda tr\u00ean. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch gi\u00fap Mexico su\u00fdt c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay&rdquo;. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Mexico thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 57 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia n\u00f3i th\u00eam: &ldquo;T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd ra s\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng b\u1ea3o h\u1ecd r\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ecbu m\u1ecdi s\u1ee9c \u00e9p ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 t\u00f4i, c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. N\u1ebfu th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00f2n thua th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u00f4m nay h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c, Mexico \u0111ang tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. H\u1ecd th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u01afCV n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd nh\u1ea5t cho ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch l\u00e0 Brazil.<br />\r\n<strong>Video: \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</strong><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span><br />\r\n<img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height: 220px;\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sat-thu-lozano-noi-gi-sau-khi-choc-thung-luoi-dt-duc-421-188761.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/sat-thu-lozano-noi-gi-sau-khi-choc-thung-luoi-dt-duc.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sat-thu-lozano-noi-gi-sau-khi-choc-thung-luoi-dt-duc-421-188761.html\">S\u00e1t th\u1ee7 Lozano n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c?</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Hirving Lozano \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thua-mexico-mats-hummels-ly-giai-viec-hang-thu-dt-duc-choi-te-465-188763.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/thua-mexico-mats-hummels-ly-giai-viec-hang-thu-dt-duc-choi-te.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thua-mexico-mats-hummels-ly-giai-viec-hang-thu-dt-duc-choi-te-465-188763.html\">Thua Mexico, Mats Hummels l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7</span><br />\r\nMats Hummels \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn thua Mexico.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thua-mexico-dt-duc-vuong-loi-nguyen-nha-vo-dich-tai-world-cup-465-188759.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/thua-mexico-dt-duc-vuong-loi-nguyen-nha-vo-dich-tai-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thua-mexico-dt-duc-vuong-loi-nguyen-nha-vo-dich-tai-world-cup-465-188759.html\">Thua Mexico, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u01b0\u1edbng l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i World Cup</span><br />\r\n\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ee9 ba li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp sau khi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 thua Mexico.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-duc-vs-mexico-vinh-danh-nhung-nguoi-dan-ong-dung-cam-421-188758.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/du-am-duc-vs-mexico-vinh-danh-nhung-nguoi-dan-ong-dung-cam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-duc-vs-mexico-vinh-danh-nhung-nguoi-dan-ong-dung-cam-421-188758.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico: Vinh danh nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m</span><br />\r\nD\u01b0 \u00e2m \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a khu v\u1ef1c CONCACAF. C\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Mexico \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eddi v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng noi g\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-duc-01-mexico-421-188757.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-duc-01-mexico.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-duc-01-mexico-421-188757.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico</span><br />\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng F VCK World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"284","checkdouble":"188768"},{"date":"03:17 18/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-brazil-11-thuy-si.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng E VCK World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- 12 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u1eeba qua ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t, Brazil th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 10 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Neymar \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i t\u1edbi 10 l\u1ea7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n Neymar t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i World Cup l\u00e0 Alan Shearer c\u1ee7a Anh n\u0103m 1998 (11 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Zuber-danh-dau-tung-luoi-Brazil.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Zuber \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n- Steven Zuber \u0111\u00e3 tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o 6 b\u00e0n sau 6 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t cho Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 (4 b\u00e0n, 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- T\u00ednh c\u1ea3 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Philippe Coutinho tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u0129, Brazil \u0111\u00e3 ghi 37 b\u00e0n t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m t\u1ea1i World Cup t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1966 t\u1edbi nay, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 11 h\u01a1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- C\u1ea3 2 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a Brazil v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 t\u1ea1i World Cup \u0111\u1ec1u k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a (tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 2-2 n\u0103m 1950).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Brazil c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 13 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup, th\u1eafng 10 (h\u00f2a 3) k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1998 t\u1edbi nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- \u0110\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 sau 19 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup m\u00e0 Brazil kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng (h\u00f2a 3) t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1934 t\u1edbi nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 kh\u00f4ng thua tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup trong c\u1ea3 3 k\u1ef3 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tham d\u1ef1 (th\u1eafng 2, h\u00f2a 1).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Xherdan Shaqiri \u0111\u00e3 tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o 6 trong s\u1ed1 7 b\u00e0n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn (4 b\u00e0n, 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Brazil 1-1 Thuy Sy\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Thong-so-Brazil.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 (B\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018):</strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/18/Brazil-1-1-Thuy-Sy.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-bong-da-brazil-vs-thuy-si-bang-e-421-188756.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/brazil-vs-thuy-si-bang-e-463-188745.html\">Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 (KT): D\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed3i, Selecao \u0111\u00e0nh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chia \u0111i\u1ec3m</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"283","checkdouble":"188769"}]}